Package: datawatch
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: default-jre-headless | java17-runtime-headless, tmux (>= 3.0)
Maintainer: dmz006 <dmz006@github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/dmz006/datawatch
Description: Multi-backend AI coding session daemon
 datawatch bridges messaging platforms to AI coding sessions running in tmux.
 Message yourself to start coding tasks, receive async updates, and interact
 with sessions from anywhere.
 .
 Supports Signal, Telegram, Matrix, webhooks and more.
 Includes a Progressive Web App for real-time access via Tailscale.
